dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Willie Robinson. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Ann Richardson.
Nice to meet you, Ann. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is two zero five six.
Thank you, Ann. Could you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, my date of birth is the seventeenth of August, nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you. Is there a specific reason for your call today, Ann?
I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, I can assist you with that. Let's proceed with the details of the new vehicle.
Thank you for providing the information, Ann. I will update your policy accordingly. If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. Have a great day! Goodbye.
